Orthanc Berseker<br />
<br />
What to say about this deck else than its other name is the “do you feel lucky deck”. I guess that I spent all my bad luck in the team tournament at DragonCon cause afterwards i kept taking risks with that deck. It seems my opponent was always one savagery short of destroying my all exhausted fellowship... until I played against a guy that paired those crazy uruks with some card drawing fellowship and with more pumps. I can’t believe they waited so long to ban that Saruman, well until they did he was one hell of a double move punisher.<br />
<br />
I recently judged a open PSQ here in Montreal and some of the new players brought sites from all sets combined. One uruk player aligned hollin, deep of helm and the slopes. All I can say is that back in the days, all the shadow cultures really had their sites, something that has been lost with time I guess.<br />
<br />
