<br />
So many versions, I had to put the one with 4 bling blings! So many things said about the deck don’t change the fact that the only way to play Moria in my mind is by giving it a chance to overhwelm and to do that you need to put more than 8 minions out. Ah how I miss the time when allies could draw cards, block and even shoot most ennemies down, thats what I call a well chosen card slot. The shadow will never be the same without Nertea, can you believe I only played 2 Nerteas and no Enquea during Essen’s finals? At least I learned something from my confrontation with Gabor, the Palanthir and those little green rats are awesome with Moria.<br />
<br />
